{"tid":1429852,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"可唔可以入黎睇下？","createTime":"2019-08-07T15:02:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T15:48:04.000Z","uid":175240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8ddffe13fc220a9db117a2ab36cd81296396aabe","tid":1429852,"uid":175240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:02:45.000Z","msg":"識一啲一直好支持年輕人抗爭嘅家長<br />\n佢地無ac 但一直有留意連登<br />\n佢地有幾句說話想同大家講<br />\n代家長朋友出post關於海港城不消費行街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1.目的不明</span><br />\n<br />\n同以往唔同，目標不明確，又出師無名，且不能攻擊政府施政<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2.影響形象</span><br />\n<br />\n如果去而家嘅海港城，其實好白痴，因為根本已經無客無人流，淨返係到嘅就只有打工嘅職員，而且，一拉閂就ko，完全表達唔到任何嘢，又俾人感覺只為滋事而行動<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3.打仗無理由斷自己糧水</span><br />\n<br />\n好老實，好多平民sales到中產都好支持運動，會捐物資，會義載，又會提供醫療服務，又幫手搵地方收埋物資，如果你地咁做只會令到幫我地既人動搖，海港城係用1蚊同政府租返嚟，影響唔到吳光正嘅九倉，同埋同我地既5大訴求無關<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">切記三思而行，勿為一時衝動</span>"},{"pid":"68472b876d56c5ff05b964c50876af8f8d426602","tid":1429852,"uid":175240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:08:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7ad6118b2fc87b285b4934ec078725c6c9a52979","tid":1429852,"uid":175240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:08:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c0e4abbb82e8cea3a12f40888dab8d27523b96c4","tid":1429852,"uid":175240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:09:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f5071c680e5c6f64503478c026c206bcb1d12066","tid":1429852,"uid":175240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:09:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c96af7764d6bad01b4cd44a61d2d26f8d3a03ea4","tid":1429852,"uid":175240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:09:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9f40676b5e52b3c5daea661c972a97552dae9ff5","tid":1429852,"uid":175240,"like":0,"dislike":0